name: Consulate General of the People's Republic of China
short_desc: Handles and issues Chinese visa, Hong Kong SAR visa/entry permit, Chinese passport, travel document, and notarization and authentication. Accepts application for Hong Kong SAR passport
description: Provides consular services to Chinese citizens. Handles and issues Chinese visa, Hong Kong SAR visa/entry permit, Chinese passport, travel document, and notarization and authentication. Accepts application for Hong Kong SAR passport.
